ATLANTIC OCEAN • Northeastern Atlantic , Bay of Biscay ;
     46º35.0′ N , 7º45.5′ W ; depth 4700 m ; 24 Oct. 1967 ; ZMH P-16464
.

Pre-natatory chaetigers with modified dorsal and ventral cirri on chaeigers 1–7;
                 notably thickened, but with distalmost tip remaining fine and cirriform ( Fig. 6C
                 ). Chaetal types in pre-natatory chaetigers as in holotype .
